            . On the 29th of March about one o'clock, I followed the prisoner from the Mansion-house, and saw him put his hand into the pocket of a gentleman who turned into the <placeName id="t18300415-335-crimeloc1810">Bank</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300415-335-crimeloc1810" type="placeName" value="Bank"></interp>
