                  </persName>
            . I was near the Bank; I felt nothing at my pocket - an apple-woman called me; I missed my handkerchief - I found it on the pavement; I gave the prisoner into custody.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Two <rs id="t18300415-335-deflabel1811" type="occupation">boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-335-defend2781 t18300415-335-deflabel1811"></join>s were walking behind the gentleman; one of them took the handkerchief and threw it behind - I caught it in my hand, and threw it on the ground; another lad was taken and was in Newgate, his friends have been drinking with the officer till two o'clock in the morning, to make it up.</p>
               <p>
            
